    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@pixelastic Your addition is fine for now and your usecase.\n\nSend a PR :)\n\n---\n\nFor more information and future evolution of transformData:\n\nIn the future I would like to only provide this:\n\n``` js\ntransformData(collection) {\n  collection = collection.map(...).filter(...);\n  return collection;\n}\n```\n\nSo that you can do any crazy stuff with the collection passed. For anything lists (so hits, refinement list etc...).\n\nSee https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/issues/739 and https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/issues/739#issuecomment-164774874\n\nWe need a good name for this and stop documenting original transformData.\n",
    "created_at": "2016-03-07T14:55:56Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/903#issuecomment-193282738",
